 Recompense?","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"ثُمَّ","fr":"Puis","en":"Then","tr":"thumma","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"مَآ","fr":"ce que","en":"what","tr":"mā","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","fr":"peut faire vous savoez","en":"can make you know","tr":"adrāka","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"مَا","fr":"ce que","en":"what","tr":"mā","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"يَوْمُ","fr":"(est le) Jour","en":"(is the) Day","tr":"yawmu","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"ٱلدِّينِ","fr":"(du) Jugement","en":"(of) the Judgment","tr":"l-dīni","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":19,"verseKey":"82:19","juz":30,"arabic":"يَوْمَ لَا تَمْلِكُ نَفْسٌ لِّنَفْسٍ شَيْـًٔا ۖ وَٱلْأَمْرُ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلَّهِ","fr":"C’est le jour où aucune âme ne pourra rien pour une autre âme. Et la décision, ce jour-là, reviendra entière à Allah.","en":"It is the Day when a soul will not possess for another soul [power to do] a thing; and the command, that Day, is [entirely] with Allāh.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"يَوْمَ","fr":"(Le) Jour","en":"(The) Day","tr":"yawma","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"لَا","fr":"non","en":"not","tr":"lā","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"تَمْلِكُ","fr":"va ont puissance","en":"will have power","tr":"tamliku","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"نَفْسٌۭ","fr":"une âme","en":"a soul","tr":"nafsun","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"لِّنَفْسٍۢ","fr":"pour une âme","en":"for a soul","tr":"linafsin","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"شَيْـًۭٔا ۖ","fr":"quoi que ce soit","en":"anything","tr":"shayan","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"وَٱلْأَمْرُ","fr":"et l’Ordre","en":"and the Command","tr":"wal-amru","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","fr":"ce Jour","en":"that Day","tr":"yawma-idhin","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"لِّلَّهِ","fr":"(va être) avec Allah","en":"(will be) with Allah","tr":"lillahi","isWaqf":false}]}]